comment.brief: Calculates the inverse of a matrix
comment.full: Calculates the inverse of a matrix

returns.text: true if the inverse matrix is valid, false if it could not be calculated correctly

parameters.name: result
parameters.description: the inverse of the `value` matrix. The values are undefined if this function returns `false`
